# Vite: exposed to the client at build time. Prefix must be VITE_.
#
# Local: omit VITE_API_URL (Vite proxies /api → backend, vite.config.ts). Or:
#   VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/v1
#
# --- Production (Netlify and/or Vercel) ---
#
# Recommended when you call the API cross-origin (cookies / auth work best with a full URL):
#   VITE_API_URL=https://your-api-host/api/v1
# No need for same-origin /api/v1 unless you want it; skip SPA_PROXY_* if the SPA talks
# straight to Render (or wherever the API runs).
#
# Optional same-origin proxy (Brave / partitioned cookies — see vite middleware + Netlify redirects):
#   SPA_PROXY_API_ORIGIN=https://your-api-host
#   VITE_API_URL=/api/v1
#   Legacy alias for Netlify redirects: NETLIFY_API_ORIGIN (same value as SPA_PROXY_API_ORIGIN).
#
# List every frontend site origin on the backend FRONTEND_URL (comma-separated) for CORS/cookies.
#
# --- Link previews (Open Graph: WhatsApp, Facebook, Slack, …) ---
# Edge middleware (Vercel) and netlify/edge-functions/experience-link-preview call the SAME
# public GET your-api/api/v1/experiences/:id. They resolve the base as:
#   EXPERIENCE_META_API_URL ?? VITE_API_URL
#
# If your site env already exposes VITE_API_URL to Builds + Functions/Edge with an absolute URL
# such as https://your-api-host/api/v1 , link previews work without EXPERIENCE_META_API_URL.
# If previews are empty, add the duplicate (same string is fine):
#   EXPERIENCE_META_API_URL=https://your-api-host/api/v1
#
# Verify after deploy:
#   curl -s -A "facebookexternalhit/1.1" "https://your-site/<path>/experiences/<mongoObjectId>"
#   Expect og:title matching the listing and og:image absolute.
#
# With proxy + OAuth callbacks: Render OAUTH_CALLBACK_ORIGIN=https://your-site (see backend/.env.example).

# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/v1

# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api-host/api/v1

# EXPERIENCE_META_API_URL=https://your-api-host/api/v1

# Optional sitewide promo strip under the main nav (set on Vercel per environment)
# VITE_PROMO_BANNER_TEXT=Join our newsletter — new hosts welcome
# VITE_PROMO_BANNER_URL=https://example.com

# Footer social icons (optional — each icon is hidden when unset)
# VITE_SOCIAL_WEBSITE=https://endebeto.com
# VITE_SOCIAL_INSTAGRAM=https://instagram.com/yourhandle
# VITE_SOCIAL_LINKEDIN=https://linkedin.com/company/yourcompany
